title: Four Malacca DAP elected reps quit party
text:
More 
Four Malacca DAP elected representatives have resigned from the party, according to Oriental Daily Online today. 
The four, Kota Melaka MP Sim Tong Him, Duyong assemblyperson Goh Leong San, Bachang assemblyperson Lim Jak Wong and Kesidang assemblyperson Chin Choong Seong, were reported announcing their decision at a press conference today.
